# Cursor Rules

Read context from (in order of increasing specificity):
1. Repository: `../../repository-context/AGENTS.md`
2. Standards: `../../repository-context/docs/standards/typescript.md`
3. Collection: `../../repository-context/collections/typescript-web-service.md`
