## Cursor-Specific Settings

- Index all files except: `node_modules`, `dist`, `.cache`, `coverage`
- Use workspace-wide search for cross-file refactoring
- Enable TypeScript IntelliSense for all files

## Note

This file contains only Cursor-specific settings. For all coding conventions, read the context files listed above.

The same conventions apply whether you use Cursor, GitHub Copilot, Aider, or other AI assistants.
